---

<BaseLayout
  title="SEO Pricing & Packages - Transparent, Affordable Results | Result Marketing"
  description="Honest pricing for AI-powered long-tail SEO. From RM 2,500/month. No setup fees, no contracts, 60-day money-back guarantee. See our transparent pricing."
  locale={lang}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-mesh">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="text-accent-500 font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">Pricing</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 text-white">
          Simple, Transparent Pricing
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-secondary-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          No hidden fees. No confusing tiers. No lock-in contracts. Just honest pricing for results-driven SEO. Choose your package based on coverage needs, upgrade or downgrade anytime.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-sm">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-success-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-white font-bold">One-Time Setup Fee</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-success-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-white font-bold">Cancel Anytime</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-success-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
