          </p>
          <p class="text-secondary-400">
            Why? Because if we're not delivering value, we don't deserve your business. Simple as that.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section bg-gradient-mesh">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="card-disruptive p-12 text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">
          Ready to Get Started?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-secondary-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Schedule a free consultation. We'll review your current SEO, identify opportunities, and recommend the right package for your goals.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://wa.me/60175032281?text=Hi%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20Result%20Marketing%20services." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-success">
            Get Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/en/services" class="btn btn-secondary">
